-- Turkey Prepping Forces With Army Drills on Syria Border, AA Says
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-08-14T14:54:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/turkey-prepping-forces-with-army-drills-on-syria-border-aa-says.html
Turkey ’s military is readying its
forces on the border with Syria with drills involving tanks,
mobile missile launchers and armored personnel carriers, the
state-run Anatolia news agency reported.  The drills are being carried out by forces at the Turkish
border town of Kilis to test “battle readiness,” Anatolia
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
